Roth & Rau Reports Ebit Loss of $35 Million in the First Half

-- B y   M a r i a j o s e   V e r a
-- 
2011-08-16T07:04:20Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-16/roth-rau-reports-ebit-loss-of-35-million-in-the-first-half.html
Roth & Rau AG (R8R)  posted a loss before
interest and tax of 24.4 million euros in the first half after a
profit of 6.1 million euros in the year-ago period.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Mariajose Vera at 
 mvera1@bloomberg.net  